This is a clean-room modern Rust reimplementation of the Prometheus
TSDB storage engine. On-disk formats (chunks, WAL, persistent blocks,
index) follow Prometheus v3.x specifications to maintain wire-format
compatibility, but no code is copied from the upstream Go project.

See also the parallel C++ implementation:
https://github.com/MerlionOS/merlion-tsdb-cpp
